OL,3,CAmber wildfire alert issued following
OL,4,Cheathland blazes
OL,6,FAn Amber wildfire alert has been
OL,7,Fissued for Dorset and Wiltshire, as
OL,8,Fdry conditions increase risks.
OL,10,FThere have already been several
OL,11,Fheathland fires in the Dorset area
OL,12,Fthis year, affecting several hectares,
OL,13,Fwhich are believed to have been
OL,14,Fstarted deliberately.
OL,16,FAn Amber alert means that a wildfire
OL,17,Fcould spread quickly and easily due to
OL,18,Fthe dry conditions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
