OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776784268
OL,3,CAmber wildfire alert issued following
OL,4,Cheathland blazes
OL,6,FDorset & Wiltshire Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService said the risk is greatest on
OL,8,Flarge areas of open land, such as
OL,9,Fheathlands, fields and cliffsides.
OL,11,FGroup Manager Graham Kewley said:
OL,12,F"While the dry, warm weather is very
OL,13,Fwelcome, it does mean the ground and
OL,14,Ffoliage are dry, leading to a greater
OL,15,Frisk of fire spreading if something
OL,16,Fhappens to cause ignition.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
