OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776784268
OL,3,CAmber wildfire alert issued following
OL,4,Cheathland blazes
OL,6,F"We would urge anyone going out and
OL,7,Fabout in our beautiful countryside
OL,8,Fover the coming days to take extra
OL,9,Fcare and be vigilant, follow our
OL,10,Fadvice to bring a picnic, not a
OL,11,Fbarbecue, and avoid having campfires
OL,12,Fon heathland or in woodlands."
OL,14,FA fire on Sandford Heath, near
OL,15,FWareham, in March destroyed an area
OL,16,Fthe size of 10 football pitches.
OL,18,FConservationists said it caused damage
OL,19,Fto protected habitat at the start of
OL,20,Fthe breeding season for many animals.
