OL,3,CAmber wildfire alert issued following
OL,4,Cheathland blazes
OL,6,FAs 60 firefighters battled the flames,
OL,7,Fa further two fires were reported at
OL,8,Fnearby Great Ovens Hill.
OL,10,FTop tips for staying fire safe while
OL,11,Fout and about include:
OL,13,FWhen calling the Fire & Rescue Service
OL,14,Fpeople are urged to:
OL,16,FIf you see any suspicious fire setting
OL,17,Fbehaviour in progress, call 999 and
OL,18,Fask for the Police.
